node.text:
Happy Halloween! I thought it was perfect to share this recipe and bring you all into the kitchen with me! So easy to make and honestly the best caramel apples I have ever had!😍 
Ingredients: 
5 small apples.
1 cup of maple syrup.
1/3 cup of canned coconut cream 
1 tablespoon of coconut oil 
1 pinch of sea salt. 
Optional Toppings: 
Dark chocolate 
Chopped nuts 
Desiccated coconut 
Peanut butter 

Feliz Halloween! Pensé que era perfecto compartiendo esta receta y te llevará a la cocina conmigo! ¡Es fácil de hacer y honestamente las mejores manzanas de dulces que he tenido! Ingredientes: 5 manzanas pequeñas. 1 taza de jarabe de arce. 1/3 taza de crema de coco enlatada 1 cucharada de aceite de coco 1 con pivote de sal. Topping opcional: chocolate, nueces, mantequilla de maní....

#caramelapples #vegan #plantbased

node.title: Easy refined sugar free/vegan Caramel Apples!!

node.text: My first live with my dearest/oldest best friend @britroza 💛 I want to continue doing a live every month with a woman that has been an inspiration and role model in my life. The purpose of these are to hopefully bring you different stories/perspectives and overall have a genuine real and raw conversation! :)

node.text: 4 months ago we took out our Fijian @namotuisland crew surfing! It was their first time getting out to a real break, let alone on a board. 4 months later and all of them still have the surfing bug and ask me everyday - how are the conditions today and can we go?!! Their faces and joy still fill my heart everyday - another reminder to me that the simple things and sharing the love is what life is all about💛💛💛

node.title: Surfs up for the Namotu Crew! :)

On Wednesday we eat pink crepes!💕😂💁‍♀️ @natrevewellness 
Ingredients: 
1/2 cup of all purpose flour
1 scoop of Strawberry shortcake protein powder @natrevewellness 
1 cup of Plant Milk of choice.
1 Tablespoon melted coconut oil. 
1 teaspoon vanilla extract.
Optional but highly recommended: Peanut butter, Melted chocolate, berries and coco whip! 

Receta fácil de crepas de proteínas!  Ingredientes: 1/2 taza de harina 1/4 taza de proteína en polvo 1 taza de leche 1 cucharada de aceite de coco derretido. Agregue mantequilla de maní, chocolate y fresas para que sean increíbles!😍💓

node.text: Same same but different.💓 Lo mismo pero diferente! Nuestros viejito casa. 🥺So surreal being back at our old house. Mom and dad designed it from the ground up and poured their whole heart into this property where we spent a total of 14 years filled with love. Crecí en esta casa y vivimos aquí durante un total de 14 años.  Tan especial estar de vuelta.🤍🤍🤍

node.text:
There is no other place in the world where you feel more connected to nature.🦋 @laparioscr is an eco lodge in one of the last low land rainforests left in the world. Beyond special being back to the place where I grew up and to see animals are thriving because of the education and support of local communities and businesses.🙏❤️ Thank you for having us @laparioscr !!

No hay otro lugar en el mundo donde te sientas más conectado con la naturaleza.. @Laparioscr es un hotel ecológico en una de las últimas selvas tropicales de tierras bajas que quedan en el mundo.  Más allá de ser especial, estar de regreso al lugar donde crecí y ver que los animales prosperan gracias a la educación y el apoyo de las comunidades y empresas locales.🙏❤️

Mornings are macha better here. ;) @natrevewellness Iced macha latte with an extra energy boost + protein! A 3 for 1! This has been my go to pre and post surf/workout pick me up! All you need is plant milk, @natrevewellness vanilla protein(this makes it extra creamy!), a good quality powdered macha and ice! (Optional sweetener of choice.) 

Las mañanas son mejores aquí. 💚Aquí está una de mis bebidas favoritas para obtener energía y proteínas ! macha latte helado! ¡Todo lo que necesitas es leche, proteína de vainilla @natrevewellness, macha en polvo y hielo! :)
